module: Module-level comment: The DE1_SoC_QSYS_cpu_mult_cell module implements a 32-bit multiplier using partial products on Cyclone V FPGA. It inputs two 32-bit values, uses two instances of `altera_mult_add` to compute lower and partial upper products, and combines these for the final result. It handles synchronization with a clock and resets using an active low signal.
